etomica.data.meter

Class MeterPressureTensor

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.data.meter.MeterPressureTensor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDataSource, IEtomicaDataSource

    public class MeterPressureTensor
extends java.lang.Object
implements IEtomicaDataSource
    Meter for evaluation of the soft-potential pressure tensor in a box. This should only be used when using an MC Integrator. For MD, use a MeterPressureTensorFromIntegrator.
